<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>
        Reset Your Password
    </title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            text-align: center;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        header {
            background-color: rgb(75, 63, 107);
            color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        header img {
            max-width: 100px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            display: block;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #333;
        }

        h3 {
            color: #777;
        }

        footer {
            background-color: rgb(75, 63, 107);
            color: #fff;
            padding: 10px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;">
    <div style="background-color: #f5f5f5; padding: 20px;">
        <img src="https://app.snapurl.in/logo.png" alt="SnapURL"
            style="max-width: 200px; display: block; margin: 0 auto;">
    </div>
    <div style="background-color: #ffffff; padding: 20px;">
        <h1>Reset Your Password</h1>
        <p>You are receiving this email because we received a password reset request for your SnapURL account. If
            you
            did not request this change, please ignore this email.</p>
        <p>Click the button below to reset your password. If you're having trouble, copy and paste the URL below
            into
            your web browser:</p>
        <p><a href="<%= resetLink %>"
                style="text-decoration: none; background-color: #007bff; color: #fff; padding: 10px 20px; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block; margin-top: 20px;">Reset
                Your Password</a></p>
    </div>
    <footer>
        &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> SnapURL. All rights reserved.
    </footer>
</body>

</html>